{"tid":1064611,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"牌照都未有！香港版小米手機突然爆出 Mi Pay 程式，無得刪？","createTime":"2019-03-16T16:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T17:48:36.000Z","uid":41818,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"87a5cc88c86f675200a7ad78abc5bb8b615d9e37","tid":1064611,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2019-03/16/212568/keithyim_1_d4df89f48c18bfc8ed945712d762a359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-03%2F16%2F212568%2Fkeithyim_1_d4df89f48c18bfc8ed945712d762a359.jpg&h=e5da081a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前我哋講過，財經界傳得好厲害，小米金融會係其中一個獲得香港虛擬銀行牌照，以後除了賣手機、水煲、電飯煲，小米更可能香港發信用卡、放債、甚至連類似八達通嘅電子錢包都撈埋？你好想用，定好驚呀？傳聞歸傳聞，牌照都未有，小米強行把 Mi Pay 小米支付安裝係小米嘅香港版手機，無得刪！大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n自動更新 Google Play 爆出來<br />\n<br />\n若果你手中有一部小米手機香港版，又係 Google Play 更新手機嘅 App，你會發現，突然多咗一個 App 叫「Mi Pay 小米支付」。中國大陸不同手機廠都有自己嘅支付工具，不過，香港要攪呢 D 服務，一定要申請相關牌照，小米，係呢篇文章發佈時呢一刻，先唔好講根本傳聞嘅虛擬銀行牌照名單仲未出，連儲值支付工具牌照都無申請，無啦啦係全港小米手機爆呢個 App 出來，攪乜呀！<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，Mi Pay 其實原來一直存在於小米手機嘅 ROM 裡入面，不過沒有顯示出來。因為他們把 M iPay 放上 Google Play Store，又推出新版本，呢個 Mi Pay 自動爆出來！喂喂喂，到底小米手機香港版裡面，仲有幾多收埋咗，唔話畀用家知嘅 Apps，呢 D Apps 有無係背後做緊乜??<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2019-03/16/212568/keithyim_3_b1148f931ffa6a6efe134d85d98ff8ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-03%2F16%2F212568%2Fkeithyim_3_b1148f931ffa6a6efe134d85d98ff8ad.jpg&h=ae1e0587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 係香港版嘅小米手機，更新手機 App，就會爆出 Mi Pay，而呢個  App 係無得刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2019-03/16/212568/keithyim_3_df3e6ff2f643ae63ae8936bc93647b10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-03%2F16%2F212568%2Fkeithyim_3_df3e6ff2f643ae63ae8936bc93647b10.jpg&h=d6891b09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 傳聞小米都申請香港虛擬銀行牌照，但相關嘅 App 做到是是但但，電郵聯絡只係一個 Gmail，咁大間公司，攪乜呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2019-03/16/212568/keithyim_3_e0ba0eef85bcb8a220751608c3f6707a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-03%2F16%2F212568%2Fkeithyim_3_e0ba0eef85bcb8a220751608c3f6707a.png&h=f62b2b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲  Mi Pay 會存取你嘅聯絡人，仲會可以控制撥打電話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/212568/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4568%2F212568%2F1%2F&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk9ey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=474059e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/212568/1/</a>"},{"pid":"78183664b5c23c98cce1ec0dc6637500c05a3750","tid":1064611,"uid":12628,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/p0RDMJGgMXF96/200w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fp0RDMJGgMXF96%2F200w.gif&h=d4f28dc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f42443ff09c887d9cb966f8bbf144117c67c2be","tid":1064611,"uid":57,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:05:27.000Z","msg":"同google pay/ apple pay有乜分別？"},{"pid":"20b903e4578db432561b3be00169df18f86441b2","tid":1064611,"uid":46151,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"6f42443ff09c887d9cb966f8bbf144117c67c2be","tid":1064611,"uid":57,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:05:27.000Z","msg":"同google pay/ apple pay有乜分別？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:08:12.000Z","msg":"呢個有資料北京備份服務囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b66a576ead555f9bfc6c30f85d086b3f2434d6","tid":1064611,"uid":57,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"20b903e4578db432561b3be00169df18f86441b2","tid":1064611,"u